  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the sliced pork and cook until browned, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced scallions, cabbage, and shiitake mushrooms to the skillet and cook until the vegetables are tender, about 4-5 minutes.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the cornstarch, soy sauce, sugar, and white pepper.",
    "Add the cornstarch mixture to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until the sauce has thickened.",
    "Warm the mu-shu pancakes according to the package instructions.",
    "Assemble the wraps by spooning the pork and vegetable mixture onto a pancake, followed by a sprinkle of green onions and sesame seeds.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
